Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say, these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, question 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose there was a single bacteria in this cup.
