Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say, after one minute, there's two bacteria.\NIn two minutes, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In three minutes, it became eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The bacteria continues dividing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In one hour the cup is completely full.
