Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the one hour
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a point where the cup is exactly half full.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This point where the cup precisely half full
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,how many minutes from the start is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please think now. You have 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This bacteria has a property of doubling each minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can think about this in the opposite way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That each minute it continually halves.
